goodwill that may lead to better mutual understanding between the
American and the Soviet people,'' said Ronald D. Leong, Parker
Brothers' vice president for marketing.
   Parker Brothers intends to unveil the newest version of Monopoly
in mid-October. More than 100 million copies of the game have been
sold worldwide since it was first marketed 53 years ago.
