<HEAD>Panel Calls For Improved Education, Training</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A panel of business and academic executives
says next president must make improved education and training a
national priority to turn around what they call the wasting of
American talent.
   ``Too much of our human talent is being wasted, and a growing
proportion of the next generation is slipping beyond the reach of
the institutions and values of our society,'' the Business-Higher
