Chicago Mercantile Exchange.
   Live cattle were .10 cent lower to .30 cent higher with October
at 71.02 cents a pound; feeder cattle were .02 cent lower to .43
cent higher with September at 80.15 cents a pound; hogs were .22
cent lower to .10 cent higher with October at 40.30 cents a pound;
